The '''Keg''' is a type of [[Crafting#Artisan Equipment|Artisan Equipment]] used to make [[Artisan Goods]]. A Keg is the reward for completing the {{Bundle|Artisan||y}} '''or''' the {{Bundle|Brewers||y}}. Four Kegs can be obtained as the 19th prize from the [[Mayor's Manor#Prize Machine|Prize Machine]] (50% chance).

